| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0628 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6c7428f4-2d34-5bb6-8332-8eb6c6147e18"
